2.2.2 Strains
With displacements known at all points within the element the âstrainsâ at any point can be determined. These will always result in a relationship that can be written in matrix notation asâ  Îµ = Su (2.13) where S is a suitable linear differential operator. Using Eq. (2.1), the above equation can be approximated by Îµ â Îµ = BË e Ë u (2.14) with B = SN (2.15)
