If the functional is âquadraticâ, i.e., if the function u and its derivatives occur in powers not exceeding 2, then Eq. (3.63) reduces to a standard linear form similar to Eq. (3.7), i.e., â Ë â¡ Ku + f = 0 Ë âu (3.64)

